items.name: Rough Spool of Thread
items.description: A spool of thread made from fibers. Can be used to make cloth strips.

items.name: Rough Stripped Wood
items.description: Strips of wood taken from a log from a tree. A skilled carpenter could form these into a plank to be used in construction or other crafting recipes.

items.name: Rough Plank
items.description: A plank of wood crafted from stripped wood

items.name: Basic Mushroom
items.description: A plump mushroom that looks edible and quite hearty. Probably better cooked.

items.name: Plain Mushroom Skewer
items.description: Mushrooms roasted on a fire skewered on a stick

items.name: Basic Clay Lump
items.description: A lump of clay. Could be used to build or craft something, or even pave the ground.

items.name: Tree Sap
items.description: A small amount of sticky tree resin

items.name: Pitch
items.description: A sticky material made by processing tree sap in a kiln

items.name: Basic Berry
items.description: A juicy edible berry. Probably better cooked.

items.name: Basic Fertilizer
items.description: A basic fertilizer made at a farming station.

items.name: Training Shortsword
items.description: A flimsy wooden sword. Could be discarded if you could find something better.

items.name: Knapped Flint
items.description: A small shard of flint rock. Brittle but sharp.

items.name: Flint Tool Bundle
items.description: A bundle that contains all the tools you'll need to get started.

items.name: Depleted Automata's Heart
items.description: A depleted Automata's Heart used by Wisp. This heart could be filled with energy to more efficiently power your body.

items.name: Flint Bow
items.description: A bow made from flint.

items.name: Stick
items.description: A regular stick harvested from bushes or striplings. Could be used for crafting or building.

items.name: Basic Flower
items.description: A flower that could be ground up to make pigment or used to make tea

items.name: Basic Pigment
items.description: Pigment made from flowers. Could be used for ink or certain clothing

items.name: Basic Starbulb Plant
items.description: Can be husked into Starlight Onion to get or Starlight Onion Seeds to replant

items.name: Basic Starbulb Seeds
items.description: Can be grown into a Basic Onion Plant in a farming field

items.name: Basic Starbulb
items.description: A Starlight Onion. Maybe a cook could make something good out of this!

items.name: Basic Crop Oil
items.description: Oil made from mashing starbulbs. Could be used to make equipment at a scholar station.

items.name: Plain Roasted Fish
items.description: Filets from a fresh water fish roasted on a fire

items.name: Plain Mashed Bulbs
items.description: Mashed potatoes. Tasty and filling but not overly interesting

items.name: Plain Fish and Bulbs
items.description: Fish arranged in a dish with salty fried potatoes. Delicious and filling

items.name: Plain Berry Pie
items.description: Smells delicious. You can hardly wait to eat it.

items.name: Plain Raw Berry Pie
items.description: An uncooked pie. Bake it in an oven to eat it!

items.name: Rough Wood Log
items.description: A cross section of a tree trunk harvested from trees or fallen trunks. Could be used to build or craft something.

items.name: Rough Wood Trunk
items.description: Can be processed into timber or cut into logs

items.name: Basic Amber Resin
items.description: Pure Resin from a tree. Could be used to make wood polish.

items.name: Rough Tree Bark
items.description: A piece of tree bark. Could be used to make brown or a leatherworking station.

items.name: Basic Citric Berry
items.description: A berry full of citric acid. Could be used by a scholar to make a solvent for refining metal.
